var title_f6_12_6343="Left subclavian artery GCA";
var content_f6_12_6343=[" <div id=\"graphicsToolbar\">",
"  <div id=\"graphicsCopy\">",
"   &copy;2013 UpToDate",
"   <sup>",
"    &reg;",
"   </sup>",
"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"graphicsLinks\">",
"   <a href=\"?imageKey=RHEUM%2F73553&amp;source=image_view&amp;view=print&amp;elapsedTimeMs=1\" onclick=\"\">",
"    <img alt=\"Print this page\" src=\"./../images/icn_print.myextg\" title=\"Print this page\"/>",
"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"icontxt textLink\" href=\"?imageKey=RHEUM%2F73553&amp;source=image_view&amp;view=print&amp;elapsedTimeMs=1\" onclick=\"\" title=\"Print this page\">",
"    Print",
"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"etacLink\" href=\"#\">",
"    <img alt=\"Email graphic(s)\" src=\"./../images/icn_email.myextg\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\"/>",
"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"icontxt textLink etacLink\" href=\"#\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\">",
"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 524px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Narrowing of the left subclavian artery in giant cell arteritis",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 504px; height: 406px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Angiogram of the left subclavian artery in GCA, showing several areas of severe vascular narrowing but a proliferation of small blood vessels forming excellent collateral circulation. The long, smooth arterial tapering in large-vessel GCA is often not amenable to revascularization interventions, such as angioplasty or stent placement. Those types of interventions are rarely necessary.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     <p>",
"      &nbsp;",
"     </p>",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Courtesy of John H Stone, MD, MPH.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
"</div>"].join("\n");
